<P>
   DEMS-GOP-ELIAN (Washington) _ Democratic National Chairman
Joseph J. Andrew, seeking to bolster Vice President Al Gore's
campaign in Florida, accuses the state's Republican Party of
exploiting the bitter custody battle over 6-year-old Elian
Gonzalez. Andrew releases a GOP fund-raising letter telling
Floridians that their donations to the party will serve as a
``powerful force against the Democrats and liberals who act
cowardly before the intimidating tactics'' of Fidel Castro. By
STEWART M. POWELL
