   The question now is what remedies the judge should prescribe.
</P>
<P>
   ``Break the company up,'' some suggest. In theory it sounds
attractive, but in practice it would be like trying to remove
unwanted software from your Windows PC _ a drawn-out process that
never quite seems finished.
</P>
<P>
   How could one define what pieces of software the different
