<P>
   www.chron.com/content/hcitalk/chat/index.html &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Clean up closets overstuffed with sweaters, shoeboxes full of
photographs and a jumble of weekend sporting equipment. Then tackle
the piles of papers on the desk. You can chat with LaNita
Filer-Jones, an organization expert. &QL; 
