<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    CLINTON, GATES ALL SMILES AT WHITE HOUSE VISIT
 &HT;    Eds: Correcting Clinton quotes throughout.
 &HT;    With E-COMMERCE. Moving in (w) Washington and (f) financial
categories.
