money for me,'' said Paolo Capoferri, who runs a small Italian food
importing business in Bridgewater, after receiving 206 shares of
Met Life on Wednesday. ``It never crossed my mind that I might get
some stock out of this.'' (Nancy Wegard/The New York Times)
