<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-MEXICO-IMMIGRATION-LADN </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
IMMIGRATION, NAFTA TOPICS IN MEXICO RACE
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By DOMINIC BERBEO 
c.2000 Los Angeles Daily News 
<TEXT>
<P>
   LOS ANGELES _ The North American Free Trade Agreement should be
revised to ease immigration laws and protect Mexican workers
